When that line was originally committed (in, uh, 2017), it came with this additional comment:

  // FIXME: all non-x86 targets need unwind tables, however, LLVM currently does
  // not know how to emit them.

https://github.com/llvm/llvm-project/commit/f561abab56801665997217099e5652e625e81cb2#diff-27605951dacea62a60c5338b839b6c25R227

However, the comment was since removed.  And the defaults left unchanged.
